copy.meta_title: Den of Wolves (DoW) - The ultimate co-op FPS heist game
copy.meta_description: Den of Wolves (DoW) - The co-op heist FPS from the creator of PAYDAY: The Heist and PAYDAY 2. Espionage, sabotage, and assassinations in a techno-thriller future. Learn more here.
copy.home_info_body: A co-op heist FPS from the creator of PAYDAY: The Heist & PAYDAY 2, set in a techno-thriller future. Gather your friends to plan and execute corporate espionage, sabotage, and assassinations.
copy.home_form_title: BE THE FIRST TO GET INTEL
copy.home_form_body_success: Your email was successfully added to the newsletter list.
copy.home_sliced_text:
Enter Midway City, the city of opportunity. Corporations here pay well for surgical hits against their competition, and you’re here to secure the bag. It’s a cutthroat gig job market, designed to allow companies plausible deniability – but you know how to play the game.

Gather your team, acquire the intel and the gear, and execute your plan. Here, there is no country or creed. Loyalty is fickle. All that matters is the next score. This is the Den of Wolves.
copy.home_popup_body: You want the real stuff? I can get you access to everything if you help me get what I need. See you on the other side.
